Package jmetal.base.variable

Class Summary
ArrayInt Implements a decision variable representing an array of integers.
ArrayReal Implements a decision variable representing an array of real values.
Binary This class implements a generic binary string variable.It can be used as a base class other binary string based classes (e.g., binary coded integer or real variables).
BinaryReal This class extends the Binary class to represent a Real variable encoded by a binary string
Int This class implements an integer decision variable
Permutation Implements a permutation of integer decision variable
Real This class implements a Real value decision variable
VariableFactory This class is intended to be used as a static Factory to obtains variables.
